<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Email Verification - Pairova</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3B82F6 0%, #2563EB 100%);
      padding: 40px 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .logo {
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin: 0;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }
    .logo-img {
      max-width: 180px;
      height: auto;
      margin: 0 auto 10px;
      display: block;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
    }
    .greeting {
      font-size: 24px;
      color: #333333;
      margin: 0 0 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .message {
      color: #666666;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin: 0 0 30px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .otp-container {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3B82F615 0%, #2563EB15 100%);
      border: 2px solid #3B82F6;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .otp-label {
      color: #666666;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .otp-code {
      font-size: 42px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #3B82F6;
      letter-spacing: 12px;
      margin: 10px 0;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
    }
    .otp-expiry {
      color: #999999;
      font-size: 13px;
      margin: 10px 0 0;
    }
    .verify-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3B82F6 0%, #2563EB 100%);
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 16px 40px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 20px 0;
      transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
    }
    .verify-button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4);
    }
    .or-divider {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0;
      position: relative;
    }
    .or-divider::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      top: 50%;
      height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #e9ecef, transparent);
    }
    .or-text {
      background: #ffffff;
      padding: 0 20px;
      color: #999999;
      font-size: 14px;
      position: relative;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    .warning {
      background-color: #fff3cd;
      border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 30px 0;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .warning-text {
      color: #856404;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
    }
    .footer-text {
      color: #999999;
      font-size: 13px;
      margin: 5px 0;
    }
    .footer-link {
      color: #3B82F6;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .footer-link:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    .divider {
      height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #e9ecef, transparent);
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <img src="{{logoUrl}}" alt="Pairova Logo" class="logo-img" />
      <h1 class="logo">Pairova</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <h2 class="greeting">Welcome to Pairova!</h2>
      
      <p class="message">
        Thank you for signing up. To complete your registration and verify your email address, 
        you can either click the button below or use the verification code.
      </p>
      
      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{verificationLink}}" class="verify-button">
          ✓ Verify Email Address
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="or-divider">
        <span class="or-text">OR ENTER CODE MANUALLY</span>
      </div>
      
      <div class="otp-container">
        <p class="otp-label">Your Verification Code</p>
        <div class="otp-code">{{code}}</div>
        <p class="otp-expiry">⏱ Valid for 15 minutes</p>
      </div>
      
      <p class="message">
        Click the button above for instant verification, or enter the code on the verification page 
        to activate your account and get started with our platform.
      </p>
      
      <div class="divider"></div>
      
      <div class="warning">
        <p class="warning-text">
          <strong>⚠️ Security Notice:</strong> If you didn't create an account with Pairova, 
          please ignore this email. Do not share this code with anyone.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <p class="message" style="margin-top: 30px;">
        Need help? Contact our support team at 
        <a href="mailto:support@pairova.com" class="footer-link">support@pairova.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p class="footer-text">
        <strong>Pairova</strong> - Connecting Talent with Opportunities
      </p>
      <p class="footer-text">
        &copy; {{year}} Pairova. All rights reserved.
      </p>
      <p class="footer-text">
        This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>


